OL,3,CConcerns raised over ALN funding in
OL,4,CWelsh schools as demand expected to
OL,5,Cincrease
OL,7,FParents, teachers, councils and
OL,8,Fcampaigners have raised concerns about
OL,9,Fa lack of funding for children with
OL,10,Fadditional learning needs (ALN) in
OL,11,FWales.
OL,13,FWelsh local authorities will spend
OL,14,Faround #668 million this year on ALN
OL,15,Fprovision in schools - an 87% increase
OL,16,Fover the past decade, but there are
OL,17,Fgrowing concerns that this does not
OL,18,Fcome close to meeting the needs of
OL,19,Fpupils.
