OL,3,CConcerns raised over ALN funding in
OL,4,CWelsh schools as demand expected to
OL,5,Cincrease
OL,7,FThere are currently 43,000 children in
OL,8,FWales listed as having additional
OL,9,Flearning needs but it's thought many
OL,10,Fmore are undiagnosed and the number is
OL,11,Fexpected to increase over the coming
OL,12,Fyears.
OL,14,FThe National Association of Head
OL,15,FTeachers has warned that schools
OL,16,Fcannot meet the demands without more
OL,17,Fsupport from the Welsh Government.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G2/8
