OL,3,CConcerns raised over ALN funding in
OL,4,CWelsh schools as demand expected to
OL,5,Cincrease
OL,7,FIn a statement, the union said: "There
OL,8,Fis a growing mismatch between the
OL,9,Ffunding they receive and the demands
OL,10,Fthey face amid rising costs, with the
OL,11,Fincreasing numbers of pupils with
OL,12,Fadditional learning needs chief among
OL,13,Fthem.
OL,15,F"Our last funding survey during the
OL,16,F2024/25 school year saw almost nine in
OL,17,Ften school leaders - 88% - identify
OL,18,FALN as a major factor causing
OL,19,Ffinancial pressures, up from 69% in
OL,20,F2021.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G3/8
