OL,3,CConcerns raised over ALN funding in
OL,4,CWelsh schools as demand expected to
OL,5,Cincrease
OL,7,FSpeaking to ITV Wales's Sharp End
OL,8,Fprogramme, Clare Anna Mitchell, from
OL,9,FSwansea, said her 11-year-old
OL,10,Fdaughter, Dakota, and many others like
OL,11,Fher were being let down by an under-
OL,12,Ffunded system.
OL,14,F"The teachers do their best. We're by
OL,15,Fno means having a go at the schools,
OL,16,Fthey do their absolute best," she said.
OL,18,F"The local authorities do what they
OL,19,Fcan with the money they've got, but we
OL,20,Fneed more money."
