OL,7,FShe added: "I think a lot of ALN
OL,8,Fchildren cope, just about, in school.
OL,9,FA lot of ALN children don't cope.
OL,11,F"But coping is almost the best you can
OL,12,Fhope for at the moment. Thriving is
OL,13,Fwhere we want our children to be in
OL,14,Fschool and they are nowhere near
OL,15,Fthriving across the board."
