OL,3,CConcerns raised over ALN funding in
OL,4,CWelsh schools as demand expected to
OL,5,Cincrease
OL,7,FIn a statement the Welsh Government
OL,8,Fsaid: "Our Final Budget prioritises
OL,9,FALN provision for learners and the
OL,10,Fstaff who support them. There is
OL,11,F#20.3m in additional funding for ALN
OL,12,Flearners, contributing to overall
OL,13,Finvestment of #74m.
OL,15,F"We also recognise the pressures on
OL,16,Fschools and essential public services
OL,17,Fand have increased our funding to
OL,18,Flocal authorities by 4.5%, providing
OL,19,F#6.6bn in the next financial year."
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G7/8
